    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Study of the interpretation of facial features with respect to qualities of mind or character, shown by peculiarities of configuration or cast or characteristic expression.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000042061/Webster's Third New International Dictionary (1961)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Estudio de la interpretación de los rasgos faciales con respecto a cualidades de entendimiento o carácter, mostradas por peculariedades de configuración o forma o expresiones características.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>De studie van de interpretatie van gelaatstrekken met betrekking tot de eigenschappen van de geest of het karakter, aangetoond door de eigenaardigheden van de vorm of het model van het gezicht of een karakteristieke uitdrukking.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
